OL,5,BWHAT I REALLY, REALLY WANTGby          
OL,6,GCatherine, seven, St Anne's, Finaghy   
OL,7,CI have a little four-year-old brother  
OL,8,Ccalled Liam who is not very well. He   
OL,9,Ccannot see or hear or walk properly. He
OL,10,Ccan walk when supported by myself or my
OL,11,Csisters but mostly he uses a wheelchair
OL,13,CI would really, really want my brother 
OL,14,Cto get better because I love him very  
OL,15,Cmuch. Liam is very funny when he makes 
OL,16,CDonald Duck noises for me. I'm glad he 
OL,17,Cis my brother.                         
